            <title>[PIG-5226] PreprocessorContext.java can deadlock forever with large stderr</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-5226</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This code can deadlock on *nix (not sure about Windows...) because of how it&apos;s using &lt;tt&gt;Runtime.exec()&lt;/tt&gt; (ie, stderr fills up its buffer and everything hangs). &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Problematic snippet of code:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/pig/blob/38c835ed702799f69dc2fa1ad0fbeab25e42c111/src/org/apache/pig/tools/parameters/PreprocessorContext.java#L238-L272&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/pig/blob/38c835ed702799f69dc2fa1ad0fbeab25e42c111/src/org/apache/pig/tools/parameters/PreprocessorContext.java#L238-L272&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
